title: endometrium2_cancer_G1
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted with Trizol Reagend according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to Affymetrix protocol  from 5-8ug of total RNA (Gene Expression Analysis Technical Manual, Affymertix).
hyb_protocol: 15ug of fragmented cRNA were hybridized on HGU133A microarray (Affymetrix). Hybrydization was performed for 16h at 45C. Gene chip was washed and stained with use  GeneChip® Fluidics Station 450 - protocol EukGE-WS2v4 .
scan_protocol: Scan was made with use of GeneArray Scanner G2500A
data_processing: The data were analyzed with Affymetrix GeneChip Command Console (AGCC) Software,  PL-Grid (http://www.plgrid.pl/) , GeneSpring 13.0 (Agilent Technologies UK Limited, South Queensferry, UK)
